org.opennebula.client.user

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opennebula.client.PoolElement
      • org.opennebula.client.user.User

  • public class User
extends PoolElement
    This class represents an OpenNebula User. It also offers static XML-RPC call wrappers.
